{
  "stem": "2539.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- but I had a wonderful life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a circle of friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the place, all the musicals, all the theaters-- not only saw them with friends, but discussed them with friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- it was paradise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It-- Vienna is a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of my friends, one friend in particular, had a car-- was a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Every weekend we drove around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was the best life I've had so far, was in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It really was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, after I graduated, I had to make a decision.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was no need for me to stay in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Vienna was not my town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had nothing to-- to-- to do in Vienna, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I got-- I was there because to get my degree.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "By the way, I want to mention to you that before the war, my parents said that we will be professionals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One of us will be a lawyer, and one of us will be a doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One of us, Lola, will study in Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I'll study in Vienna, or vice versa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was my parents' plan that I overheard as a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And strange enough, after they got killed, didn't exist anymore, their wish was carried out by me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But Uncle-- Uncle Adolph, my father's brother, wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He finished up in Argentina, where he died in Buenos Aires.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He survived the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He ran away from Hitler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And his daughter is still living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I heard that happened to Lola was-- we lived in a small little room, which was a part of an apartment, in which there was-- to get to our room from the-- through the kitchen, you had to walk through a room of a doctor, who lived there with this mother, and an auntie, and an uncle.",
      "word_count": 58
    }
  ],
